{"tid":1485730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"圍住個紅衫影相，呢張相比170萬人遊行既相更加有力量","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:49:59.000Z","uid":50992,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a425ec28720429831ccf01e687755678678a58a2","tid":1485730,"uid":50992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"其實今日話就話和理非主場<br />\n但今日前線圍紅衫影果張相更加重要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝前線既努力</span></span>，證明香港人同黑警同大陸班5毛係有好大既分別!<br />\n<br />\n我明白係個MON前面想叫人走果種著急<br />\n但我相信前線，佢地知道自己點解要留<br />\n正如前線相信和理非，想保護佢地走先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多謝前線既巴絲打! 希望唔好比大家一時著急講既說話影響到!</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核爆都唔割!</span></span>"},{"pid":"eddf18e8563ecf9e9c4a758c09eb5c7a1cf677b7","tid":1485730,"uid":15696,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/8UOWx4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UOWx4k.png&h=3fcb3c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e6cdcd8c8a8654305edf93bffcdd4d36b0f47de","tid":1485730,"uid":50992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"其他捉鬼POST唔好再睇啦"},{"pid":"c15be9c8a660e4796e07afe22a1bbd92b6105186","tid":1485730,"uid":50992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"推，其他捉鬼POST唔好再睇啦"},{"pid":"90c4084b06f36220a3ab05044176897f4ea819bd","tid":1485730,"uid":50992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"前線都好好休息下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4bbe3b6d711ddcde82db9e96122c37ae6fa19c","tid":1485730,"uid":50992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:36.000Z","